(6, 'status_change_from_hr_to_process_to_hr_email_sent', 'This email will shoot when Users all documents status is change from HR To Process to HR Email Sent.', 'Users Document Status is changed.', '<p>Hello Admin,</p>\r\n<p>All documents are sent to {user_name} for filling.</p>\r\n<p>Following are the documents :</p>\r\n<p>{document_list}</p>', '2019-03-01 06:45:06'),
